{"id":466581,"date":[{"year":1965,"month":6,"day":1}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"666","ytitle":"","mtitle":"全家学英雄(儿歌)","ftitle":"","authors":["张秋生"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶奶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放映员，来咱庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银幕挂在打谷场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑语停，场上静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天放的《槐树庄》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"槐树庄上郭大娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心向着党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级仇，阶级恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级血泪记心上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱奶奶，捏紧拳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看得眼角闪泪光:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“郭大娘，好姊妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是公社顶天梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸摸身上旧鞭痕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看地主变天账，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仇和恨，不能忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我眼明心更亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举红旗，闹革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要叫后辈更坚强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头发虽白心要红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也要学你的样。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山连山，坡连坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山坡坡不见边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬石块，挑泥土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半山腰里垒梯田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的山水听调遣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坡上麦子黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山顶果林艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻一山，望一眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛羊满坡猪满圈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员连夸变得快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸听了笑得欢:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“学的大寨人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种的大寨田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们永远听党话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村能变大花园。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姊姊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小辫儿，细又长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算盘儿，噼啪响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕读学校毕了业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到队里算工账。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活挑重的干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见难她就上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工分算得清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算盘打得响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁爱沾便宜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见她心就慌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伯婶子亲爹娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管对谁都一样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱社爱得入了迷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是大伙好榜样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我呀叫她好姊姊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙叫她“李双双”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邮递员，按车铃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我哥哥，来了信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从哪里?从上海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写点啥?你听听:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“队伍进了城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹妈请放心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端着枪，来站岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霓虹灯下当哨兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下穿草鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头上顶红星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因听了毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立场越站越坚定。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习八连好传统，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我被评为五好兵。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷象我这样大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骑马挎枪打天下；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸象我这样大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站岗放哨把匪查，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我虽小，志气大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习小兵好张嘎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮队里，干活儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管好公社一群鸭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一天，后半夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽听鸭儿叫嘎嘎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提着棍，朝外跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准是恶狼来偷鸭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是叫，又是追，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把恶狼逮住了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问恶狼啥长相，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿!就是地主“烂冬瓜”。"}]}